title: FOX 26 Houston: News

creator: Fox Television Stations, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
News doesn't wait, why should you? Take FOX 26 everywhere you go! Our app connects you with top stories in and around the Houston area— complete with breaking news alerts, live video, and real-time weather forecasts.

We cover topics that matter most to you including local & national headlines, weather, sports, traffic, politics, entertainment, food, education, crime and so much more.

NEWS & VIDEO
- Breaking news delivered as fast as it breaks
- Live stream newscasts each weekday
- Streamlined content display for a user-friendly experience

WEATHER
- Gulf Coast weather updates you can count on
- Hourly conditions and 7-day forecasts so you're always prepared for your day
- Interactive radar 24 hours a day
- Fresh video updates from FOX 26’s meteorologists
- Hurricane Toolbox for disaster preparedness

SPORTS
- The latest scoop on the Texans, Rockets, Astros, Dynamo, high school sports and other Texas teams
